ariaLabel.description: The aria-label of the button element. Also used to provide the id for the SpeedDial element and its children.
ariaLabel.description_zh: button 元素的 aria-label。还用于提供 SpeedDial 元素及其子元素的 ID。

children.description: SpeedDialActions to display when the SpeedDial is open.
children.description_zh: SpeedDialActions 在 SpeedDial 打开时显示。

classes.description: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.See CSS classes API below for more details.
classes.description_zh: 覆盖或扩展应用于组件的样式。有关详细信息，请参阅下面的 CSS 类 API。

direction.description: The direction the actions open relative to the floating action button.
direction.description_zh: 操作相对于浮动操作按钮的打开方向。

FabProps.description: Props applied to the Fab element.
FabProps.description_zh: 应用于 Fab 元素的道具。

hidden.description: If true, the SpeedDial is hidden.
hidden.description_zh: 如果为 true，则 SpeedDial 处于隐藏状态。

icon.description: The icon to display in the SpeedDial Fab. The SpeedDialIcon component provides a default Icon with animation.
icon.description_zh: 要在 SpeedDial Fab 中显示的图标。SpeedDialIcon 组件提供带有动画的默认图标。

onClose.description: Callback fired when the component requests to be closed.Signature:function(event: object, reason: string) => voidevent The event source of the callback.reason Can be: "toggle", "blur", "mouseLeave", "escapeKeyDown".
onClose.description_zh: 当组件请求关闭时触发回调。Signature：function（event： object， reason： string） => voidevent callback.reason 的事件源可以是： “toggle”， “blur”， “mouseLeave”， “escapeKeyDown”。

onOpen.description: Callback fired when the component requests to be open.Signature:function(event: object, reason: string) => voidevent The event source of the callback.reason Can be: "toggle", "focus", "mouseEnter".
onOpen.description_zh: 当组件请求打开时触发回调。Signature：function（event： object， reason： string） => voidevent callback.reason 的事件源可以是： “toggle”， “focus”， “mouseEnter”。

open.description: If true, the component is shown.
open.description_zh: 如果为 true，则显示组件。

openIcon.description: The icon to display in the SpeedDial Fab when the SpeedDial is open.
openIcon.description_zh: 当 SpeedDial 打开时，在 SpeedDial Fab 中显示的图标。

sx.description: The system prop that allows defining system overrides as well as additional CSS styles.See the `sx` page for more details.
sx.description_zh: 允许定义系统覆盖以及其他 CSS 样式的系统属性。有关更多详细信息，请参阅“sx”页面。

TransitionComponent.description: The component used for the transition. Follow this guide to learn more about the requirements for this component.
TransitionComponent.description_zh: 用于过渡的组件。按照本指南了解有关此组件要求的详细信息。

transitionDuration.description: The duration for the transition, in milliseconds. You may specify a single timeout for all transitions, or individually with an object.
transitionDuration.description_zh: 转换的持续时间，以毫秒为单位。您可以为所有过渡指定单个超时，也可以单独指定一个对象超时。
transitionDuration.type: number| { appear?: number, enter?: number, exit?: number }

TransitionProps.description: Props applied to the transition element. By default, the element is based on this Transition component.
TransitionProps.description_zh: 应用于过渡元素的道具。默认情况下，该元素基于此 Transition 组件。

events.name: onClose
events.description: Callback fired when the component requests to be closed.Signature:event The event source of the callback.reason Can be: "toggle", "blur", "mouseLeave", "escapeKeyDown".
events.description_zh: 当组件请求关闭时触发回调。Signature：event callback.reason 的事件源可以是：“toggle”、“blur”、“mouseLeave”、“escapeKeyDown”。

events.name: onOpen
events.description: Callback fired when the component requests to be open.Signature:event The event source of the callback.reason Can be: "toggle", "focus", "mouseEnter".
events.description_zh: 当组件请求打开时触发回调。Signature：event callback.reason 的事件源可以是：“toggle”、“focus”、“mouseEnter”。
